<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Ethan Phillips plays the buddy and cohort of the romantic lead in "Up in 
Saratoga" at the Old Globe Theatre in San Diego. The actor was misidentified in 
the review of the show Saturday. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
