Hepburn ; Photo, Lauren Bacall ; Photo, Dean Stockwell ; Photo, Veronique Peck, 
left, Gregory, and their daughter Cecilia enjoy a chuckle during AFI encomiums. 
IRIS SCHNEIDER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
